text: Cleber Leite (13 May 1969 - 22 April 2017) was a Brazilian rower. He competed in the men's coxed four event at the 1992 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1969 births Category:2017 deaths Category:Brazilian male rowers Category:Olympic rowers of Brazil Category:Rowers at the 1992 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rio de Janeiro (city)
